name: The Invaders Strike Back
description:
Invaders are back. Invade Earth as invaders. Destroying enemies quickly and preserving invaders are the keys to get a high score. 

This game is originally made for Unity 1 week game jam, the biggest Unity game jam in Japan. Unity 1 week game jam is held in unity room. See below for the details.

https://unityroom.com/unity1weeks/15
